            "text": "<p>Being a full time model requires a lot of travel which keeps me out of the salon longer than I’d like to be. But thanks to Refuge and their amazing <a href=\"\/products\/hydrate-balance\" title=\"HYDRATE + BALANCE 3-STEP HAIR CARE SYSTEM\">Hydrate + Balance<\/a> system, combined with adorable packaging, I’m able to keep my curls hydrated and defined everywhere I go!<br\/><br\/><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/sagetheworld\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/sagetheworld\">@sagetheworld<\/a><\/p>",
